011110.text: Destack is an open source page builder that works with your existing  projects.

01133110.text:
TLDR: It's a page builder that runs locally and everything is saved in your repository.

You can use it in any React or Nextjs project. It can be setup in one page or multiple pages!

It comes with the batteries included. It packs the complete set of components from Tailblocks, Meraki UI and Hyper UI.

01133130.text:
It also supports asset uploading and form submission.

Destack is a tool to help you stop worrying about the marketing pages and focus on your project.
